<!-- Testimonials — 3 real quotes from past wedding clients per CONTENT-04. Pull-quotes use EB Garamond italic. -->
---
import Section from '@/components/ui/Section.astro';
---

<Section id="testimonials" tone="cream">
  <h2>What couples say</h2>
  <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
    <figure>
      <span class="font-serif text-5xl text-bronze leading-none" aria-hidden="true">&ldquo;</span>
      <blockquote class="font-serif italic text-lg mt-4">The photos are amazing. Thank you so much for capturing our day and all the beautiful memories. From someone who hates having their picture taken, you made it very easy. There was no rush or hassle with anything we wanted to get done. During the ceremony you were so discreet but captured all the special moments. It was such a pleasure to have you part of our day.</blockquote>
      <figcaption class="mt-6 text-sm text-ink-soft not-italic">&mdash; Louise &amp; Jonathan</figcaption>
    </figure>

    <figure>
      <span class="font-serif text-5xl text-bronze leading-none" aria-hidden="true">&ldquo;</span>
      <blockquote class="font-serif italic text-lg mt-4">Thank you for your professionalism and the care you took in capturing our special day. These photographs will last forever and will be passed down to our grandchildren and many generations after that. You're clearly very skilled judging by the quality of the pictures. I will be recommending you to anyone seeking a very skilled and professional photographer.</blockquote>
      <figcaption class="mt-6 text-sm text-ink-soft not-italic">&mdash; Preety &amp; Ayanda</figcaption>
    </figure>

    <figure>
      <span class="font-serif text-5xl text-bronze leading-none" aria-hidden="true">&ldquo;</span>
      <blockquote class="font-serif italic text-lg mt-4">Karl took photos for our wedding day and was extremely professional. My whole family commented on how comfortable they felt with him and that they barely knew he was there — which was great, because he managed to get so many candid shots of everyone looking relaxed. Such a pleasant person to work with. Thank you so much for your beautiful work, Karl!</blockquote>
      <figcaption class="mt-6 text-sm text-ink-soft not-italic">&mdash; Devon &amp; Thomas</figcaption>
    </figure>
  </div>
</Section>
